# Project Overview

Quarkus 3 CLI application (`github-stats` artifact, root Picocli command **`github`**) that collects **GitHub organization repository statistics** into CSV. Single primary flow: **`collect-stats`** (`CollectStatsCommand`). Integration tests and README invoke **`collect-stats`** directly; Picocli-generated man pages may still show **`github collect-stats`** as the full command path.

## Tech Stack

- **Runtime:** Quarkus (version from **`quarkus.platform.version`** in `pom.xml`), Java 25, Maven wrapper **`./mvnw`**
- **CLI:** Picocli via `quarkus-picocli` (`@TopCommand` on `GitHubCommand`)
- **DI:** Quarkus Arc (CDI)
- **GitHub REST:** `quarkus-github-api` (kohsuke `GitHub` / `GHRepository` — org listing, contributors, **traffic** clones/views)
- **GitHub GraphQL:** `quarkus-smallrye-graphql-client` (dynamic client + classpath query under `src/main/resources/graphql/queries/`)
- **GraphQL models:** Generated by `graphql-codegen-maven-plugin` into `clients.graphql.generated`; **forked** FreeMarker templates under `src/main/resources/graphql-codegen-templates/` (re-sync from plugin JAR when bumping `graphql.codegen.version`)
- **Mapping:** MapStruct (`GraphqlRepositoryToCsvMapper` + `mapping.fields.*` `@Named` helpers for GraphQL → CSV `model.csv.Repository`)
- **Data:** Jackson (JSON + YAML for config), Apache Commons CSV
- **Testing:** JUnit 5, Mockito, `@QuarkusTest`, `@QuarkusMainIntegrationTest`

## Package Structure

Base: `com.garethahealy.githubstats`

- **`commands`** — Picocli commands (`CollectStatsCommand`, `GitHubCommand` as `@TopCommand`)
- **`clients`** — Hand-written **`GitHubGraphQLClient`** (SmallRye GraphQL client wrapper) and **`GitHubRestClientConfig`** (produces kohsuke **`GitHub`** for REST). **Generated** GraphQL types live only under **`clients.graphql.generated`**; there is no hand-written `clients.graphql` package and no `clients.rest` package in the current tree
- **`config`** — **`GitHubConfigProperties`** (`@ConfigMapping`), **`config.jackson`** (ObjectMapper / YAML / GraphQL typing + mixins under `config.jackson.mixins`)
- **`mapping`** — `GraphqlRepositoryToCsvMapper` + **`mapping.fields`** (MapStruct `@Named` mapping beans)
- **`model.csv`** / **`model.graphql`** — CSV row record (`Repository`), GraphQL response wrapper types
- **`processor`** — e.g. `ConfigYamlProcessor` for org config YAML
- **`services`** — `GitHubOrganizationLookupService`, `GitHubRepositoryStatsService`, `GitHubContributorsLookupService`, `GitHubTrafficLookupService`, `GitHubConfigYamlService` (flat `services` package, not `services.github`)
